and sync hardening PR\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"mirror-db-security-sync-hardening\",\n      \"type\": \"bugfix\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-06-16 11:46\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 79299,\n      \"preview\": \"On 2026-06-17, after user requested non-GUI cleanup work via threads, created GitHub issues #156-#163 for remaining non-GUI rclean gaps. Implemented two PRs from origin/main bf62d996: PR #165 fixes #156 by making `clean --plan` honor ActionPlan `deleteMode`, rejecting conflicting CLI mode flags, and\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/AI/tools/rclean\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"Created non-GUI cleanup issues and PR fixes #164/#165\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"non-gui-cleanup-issues-prs-156-165\",\n      \"type\": \"bugfix\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-06-16 16:51\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 56235,\n      \"preview\": \"Bugfix: Amenities Map legend POI names were too long for the SVG legend column, so truncation now happens on whole-word boundaries with trailing separators removed. The helper `truncatePoiNameToWholeWord` uses a default display cap of 39 characters, which avoids clipped partial words in the right le\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/mutil-om\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"Amenities map legend POI names truncate on whole words\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"amenities-map-legend-poi-truncation\",\n      \"type\": \"bugfix\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-06-16 13:24\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 79300,\n      \"preview\": \"Chose the VibeGuard user-visible management page direction as a local-first `Project Operations` dashboard generated by the repo-local Codex App plugin, not a hosted telemetry/admin surface and not an unsupported custom Codex panel. The dashboard uses existing structured runtime data (`vibeguard-run\"